    poor pictures, errant marks, etc. that were either part of the original artifact, 
    or were introduced by the scanning process. We believe this work is culturally
    important, and despite the imperfections, have elected to bring it back into print 
    as part of our continuing commitment to the preservation of printed works worldwide. 
    We appreciate your understanding of the imperfections in the preservation process, 
    and hope you enjoy this valuable book. </p>

